data.description: Fantastic Craftsman Home that provides approx. 2000sf with 4 Bedrooms, and 2.5 Bathrooms. Great Open Floor plan, Gas Fireplace, and laminate flooring throughout main level. Kitchen has an Island with Eat Bar, Stainless appliances, plus Pantry. Huge Primary Suite. 2 Car Garage that has a professional partial conversion Room that includes sink with Hot/Cold water, & closet - Can be used for Office/Bedroom.  Brand New AC Unit /Heat Pump. New Yard Landscaping.    Home is close to highway access & No HOA.
